HEADWORD: portmanteau word
<hw>port*man"teau word`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>portmanteau</er>.]</ety> <def>A word formed by joining two others;
-- as, <it>smog</it> is formed from <er>smoke</er> and
<er>fog</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Wordnet 1.6</source>]</p>

